== Overview ==

CAD-score is a command-line software that constructs the Voronoi diagram
of protein atom spheres, calculates inter-atom contact surfaces
and uses them to compare protein structures of the same sequence.

A brief tutorial is available from CAD-score site:

https://bitbucket.org/kliment/cadscore/wiki/Home


== Preparing to use ==

Download the latest package from CAD-score downloads page:

https://bitbucket.org/kliment/cadscore/downloads

A compiled static executable for GNU/Linux is included in the package.
However, it is recommended to rebuild the executable
using the following command:

g++ -O3 -o bin/voroprot2 src/*.cpp


